text: Bjarne is a Nordic male name, a variant of Bjorn, and may be, *Bjarne Kallis, a Finnish politician *Bjarne Liller, a Danish jazz musician *Bjarne Melgaard, a Norwegian painter *Bjarne Møgelhøj, a Danish politician *Bjarne Pedersen, a motorcycle racer *Bjarne Pettersen, a Norwegian gymnast *Bjarne Reuter, a Danish writer *Bjarne Riis, a bicycle racer *Bjarne Stroustrup, creator of the C++ programming language *Bjarne Tromborg, a physicist ==Related pages== *Bjarni *Bjorn Category:Given names Category:Danish masculine given names Category:Norwegian masculine given names
title: Bjarne
